{"tid":2300814,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"曾經滄海","createTime":"2020-11-25T23:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T05:07:37.000Z","uid":74778,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c0fa2c12de7e8c76baa8cfd95f82d4ed406d86fe","tid":2300814,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T23:50:52.000Z","msg":"曾經滄海<br />\n<br />\n我曾經想成為陽光。但今天在一旁看海，連海浪都可以把我燒焦，成為殆盡的煙灰。灰撒在海上。<br />\n<br />\n未知生，焉知死。有了死亡，才有更好的重生。<br />\n<br />\n每個人都也不是一樣？就好似唯心論的信徒，但自己卻不自知。可是，這就是我們為人最大的力量了，想像，希望，虛妄，又重來。<br />\n<br />\n只取一瓢飲<br />\n<br />\n經歷過生離死別，經歷過崩潰和失控。這是平凡的人。想像吧，我們最會了。那把我燒焦成灰的海浪，在晚上卻是當了月光的紙尿片。"},{"pid":"ec7e14652e154699f8c8f96a0e0d97abb42f45a8","tid":2300814,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T03:10:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc540c1e932435e7c689eee2ed2d1a79f5c5b74d","tid":2300814,"uid":332452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T23:54:28.000Z","msg":"最尾一句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3caff2ff419e79b1c0933bce708f3e8582b7e4bc","tid":2300814,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc540c1e932435e7c689eee2ed2d1a79f5c5b74d","tid":2300814,"uid":332452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T23:54:28.000Z","msg":"最尾一句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T00:04:04.000Z","msg":"好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382e29cace160daedc020f5ced3606cc1d9c1cd0","tid":2300814,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T05:07:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}